All the percentages for electoral demographics are calculated by Tindak Malaysia. There is no official ethnic demographic data. Sum of percentages for electoral demographics may not attain exact 100% but the variation is kept less than 2%. TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible  for any errors or ommissions arising from the original data or its derivatives
